# Angee Dev Stack

This project has been initialized with the example `stacks/dev` template.

Start local dev:

```sh
angee dev
```

The CLI starts or reuses a local ad-hoc operator. The operator reads `.angee/angee.yaml`, leases ports, runs jobs, and supervises services.

Useful commands:

```sh
angee stack show
angee source list
angee service list
angee workflow show dev
angee logs web --follow
```
